org.archive.wayback.exception

Class BetterReplayRequestException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.archive.wayback.exception.WaybackException
          • org.archive.wayback.exception.BetterRequestException
            • org.archive.wayback.exception.BetterReplayRequestException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class BetterReplayRequestException
extends BetterRequestException
    Sub-class of BetterRequestException for instructing a redirect to ArchivalUrl for the URL on different timestamp.

    This class generates additional HTTP headers for Memento support.
